<h3 class="big">Help: web aggregators</h3>
web supports variety of aggregator functions, such as:
<b>min, max, sum, count, avg, median</b>. They can be applied in any
order to any web record attribute. For example:
<pre>
file dataset=/a/b/c |  max(file.size), min(file.size),avg(file.size),median(file.size)
</pre>
Custom map-reduce function are also supported. Please contact web 
<b><a href="https://svnweb.cern.ch/trac/CMSDMWM/newticket?component=web&summary=Request map reduce function&owner=valya">support</a></b> if you need one.
    
