<h3 class="big">Help: web special keywords</h3>
web has special <b>records</b> and <b>queries</b> keywords.
The former can be used to look-up all records in web cache, while
later shows most recent queries placed in web. The web filters
can be used with them too. For example, if you want to see if there
are any file records in web cache you can simply type:
<pre>
records | grep file.name
</pre>
    
